a player's health is at zero 
(no life bar visible) when the 
bonus level/intermission ends, 
s/he will begin the next level 
at full health (three life 
bars). So if you CAREFULLY 
hack one another, you can 
restore your health. You 
should allow the other 
character to recover after 
each swipe, otherwise you may 
throw or kick and actually 
kill the other player.

$end

