#The New Zealand Story
$info=tnzs,tnzsb
$icon=tnzs
$data
$bio
Tips and Tricks:


Occasionally when you lose
your 
last life, instead of getting 
the "GAME OVER" screen you'll 
get a message something like
this: "Welcome to Heaven"

There are three different 
heaven rounds, depending on 
the level you end on, one 
each for Rounds 4-6. The 
trick is to "get out" of 
Heaven - if you reach the 
Virgin Mary, the game ends. 
There's a secret exit out of 
each Heaven. Some are harder
to find than others. Once you 
get out, your game will 
continue as normal.

You only enter Heaven if you 
are on level 3-1 or later, and 
only if you are killed by a 
projectile weapon (rock, 
boomerang, laser, etc.) Also, 
you can only enter heaven once 
per game. Having escaped once, 
you go to hell instead (game 
over). If you are killed by a 
contact killer enemy, or by a 
spike of any sort, or by fire 
of any sort, you do not go to 
heaven. Getting killed by the 
hurry-up devil also will 
guarantee you don't go to 
heaven.

$end

