$bio
Tips and Tricks:


There is a 30,000 point bonus
awarded at the end of each
stage accomplished without
using any shuriken or bullets
(only "chens").


Bosses 1 and 4 can be killed
by simply pressing jump and
immediately shooting after
that (sort of a jumpshoot!)


At the level just before the
falling Buddhas, you'll reach
a spot between ventilation
pipes, where lots of blue
ninjas show up. Instead of
using the ninja magic,
position yourself at the right
in this tight spot then jump
back till you reach the open
area, where you can take care
of the ninjas.


On stage 3-1 and 3-2 there are
enemies that use bazookas as a
weapon. If you bump into them
by walking into them, making
the "ouch" noise for 6 to 10
times, every enemy will not
shoot for the rest of the
stage! You can just walk into
any enemy that wields a gun.
Just be careful of the guys
that have swords - they will
still kill you.


In level 3-4 at the Buddhas,
run up to them and keep
shooting. Stand there shooting
and they will move closer to
you. Just
before they bump you back, use
your magic. As soon as you use
it, rapidly tap the right,
jump and fire buttons. The
Buddhas will continue to move
over the top of you. If done
correctly, once you return to
the original state, your
character
will continue to bounce back
and forth between the Buddhas.
Remember you should still be
tapping the joystick right and
the jump and fire buttons all
rapidly and simultaneously.
Keep this up until you exit
the Buddhas from the other
side,
and then wait until they clear
the screen and finish the boss
off. 

$end

