sure they could own the
trademark on the title.


Tips and Tricks:


An undocumented feature: you 
need to have killed everything 
off in the wave except for one 
lander. There must be at least 
one humanoid on the ground. 
Wait for the lander to pick up 
the humanoid. Shoot the lander 
and catch the humanoid *just*
before it hits the ground. The 
screen will flash like mad and 
you will be awarded 2000, 
presumably for catching the 
humanoid and depositing it on 
the ground in the tiny
interval 
before the wave ends. 


If you go in to the warp gate 
and press reverse and warp at 
the same time you will make 
