#Time Pilot 84
$info=tp84
$icon=tp84
$data
$bio
Tips and Tricks:


On the first level, head 
directly to the right. After a
couple of screens, you'll see 
an unusual "V" formation of 
silver ships that resemble 
craft in Time Pilot 1, heading 
up or down. This easy-to-kill
formation gives you 8,000 
points, a good start to the 
game.


The biplane from the original 
Time Pilot makes a cameo 
appearance in TP84. To find
it, 
fly right to the water and 
harbor area. Then turn 
vertically up the screen. When 
the biplane appears (over 
water), hit it with a missile, 
and you are rewarded with a 
free player! 


This game contains many
bonuses, 
hidden and otherwise. Here is
a 
semi-complete scoring table:

 
Green enemy: 100 pts


Silver enemy on ground 
w/missile: 200 pts


Silver enemy w/missile: 500 
pts


Missile carrier: 1,000 pts


Bomb carrier: 1,000 pts


Formation of 5 (Green
enemies):
 3000(max) pts


Formation of 5 (Silver
enemies)
: 5,000 pts


Uncover hidden ground target: 
5,000 pts


Boss ship at end of level: 
5,000 pts


Shooting 8 ground targets: 
8,000 pts

$end

